Invocation Name: farm sounds
des:
Simpy ask Alexa to start Farm sounds, then Start. Its that easy!
Alexa will then pick a random sounds and you need to guess it! Fun for the little ones in your family. Once you got the answer, then say next!

Comments appreciated if you find a bug, or just want to recommend new sounds! 
Thanks for trying the skill!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
